---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About CALDON™ - Private property development across NSW since 2015.">
  <style>
    .page-header {
      padding: 180px 0 100px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: var(--subtle-accent);
    }
    
    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    
    .page-header h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .page-header p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
    
    .content-section:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: var(--subtle-accent);
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-header {
        padding: 150px 0 80px;
      }
      
      .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      .content-section {
        padding: 60px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our Story</p>
      <h1>About CALDON™</h1>
      <p>Private property development and investment across New South Wales since 2015.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>CALDON™ operates as a private property development and investment company with deep roots in the NSW market. Our focus spans regional and metropolitan New South Wales, with particular expertise across the Mid North Coast and Hunter regions, and selective opportunities in Sydney and surrounds.</p>
        <p>We maintain a reserved approach to business, working primarily with established real estate professionals, qualified investors, and strategic partners. Our operations are built on discretion, market intelligence, and the pursuit of exceptional property opportunities.</p>
        <p>Through careful site selection, strategic timing, and meticulous execution, we have built a reputation for delivering quality developments and maintaining a strong portfolio of investment assets across diverse property sectors.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>Our Approach</h2>
        <p>At CALDON™, we believe that discretion, precision, and strategic thinking drive exceptional property outcomes. Every project we undertake is evaluated through a rigorous lens of market fundamentals, risk assessment, and long-term value creation.</p>
        <p>We are not volume developers. We select opportunities carefully, execute with precision, and maintain the highest standards throughout every phase of development—from initial site identification through to project completion and beyond.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
